All the material has been deposited in the Natural History Collections, Faculty of Biology, Adam Mickiewicz University (Poznań, 
Poland
). All samples contain detailed information on the number of individuals, date of collecting, detailed locality data, the elevation of the sampling site above sea level, and the name of person who collected the sample.

Distribution maps were prepared to show the approximate limits of the distribution of each species, based on both the rich amount of recently collected material and literature data. Where possible, precise distribution ranges have been delimited (e.g. in 
Poland
).

